item.title: 2D Fall
item.description: 2D Fall can be your best time killer game ever. It’s a physics based rock falling game, with easy controls and challenging gameplay. You can also switch between different balls with multiple characteristics. Collect coins and get your balls unlocked and enjoy game. How to play Just tap right or left part of screen to control the rock fall from on plank to other. Let’s see how much you can fall.
